{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1014742, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 202276, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "拿不着自然觉着是臭的", "timestamp": 1611925295, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1014751, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 202276, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "仇富者的一个普遍特征就是穷……", "timestamp": 1611925359, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1014752, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 202276, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "仇富难道不是仇视富人的意思吗？", "timestamp": 1611925363, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1014788, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 202276, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "仇视富人，不仇视钱", "timestamp": 1611925640, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1014809, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 202276, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 哦哦这样，但仇富就是讨厌富人、不想成为，那不就是不想有钱…?", "timestamp": 1611925783, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1014838, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 202276, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 认为富人拿的是不义之财（事实上有一定正确性）", "timestamp": 1611926058, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1014840, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 202276, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 认为目前存在的富人的钱不是靠诚实劳动合法经营得来的而是通过一些灰色方法，认为他们这些先富的人把勤劳致富的门堵死了，认为自己很优秀，本可以通过勤劳致富的。\n三合一，仇富", "timestamp": 1611926058, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1014843, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 202276, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 讨厌别人成为……默认零和效应，富人赚走了本属于我们穷人的钱", "timestamp": 1611926097, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1014847, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 202276, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 现在谈这些历史问题和没法改变的问题其实很可笑，即使某种程度是对的。", "timestamp": 1611926105, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1014879, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 202276, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 如果放在历史里，其实都只能宏观看，细节几乎都是被淹没的。勤劳致富在任何时代都不是主旋律。", "timestamp": 1611926412, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1014903, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 202276, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 不是的，是敌视？", "timestamp": 1611926676, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1014993, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 202276, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "确切地说仇富针对的是生产资料，即富人靠钱生钱对穷人进行掠夺\n富人的钱再多也有花完的一天，但是“因为富人有钱所以穷人的劳动所得就要无偿分给富人一份”本来就是很荒谬的事", "timestamp": 1611927745, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1015058, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 202276, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 不劳动者不得食，我一直认为这应该是基本的社会原则", "timestamp": 1611928600, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1015098, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 202276, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 害，哪有那么多应该，eve家里不炒股没公司分红？", "timestamp": 1611929149, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1015354, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 202276, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "大家说的对，但多数人仇富的时候可能只是一种难以描述的情感吧，不会想到这么多？", "timestamp": 1611932182, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1015801, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 202276, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 在马克思主义诞生之前，英国迷惘的卢德主义者将自己失业的愤怒砸向取代了他们工作的大机器；\n在得不到先进的理论武装的情况下，无产阶级只能凭借**自发**的朴素的感情反抗资产阶级的压迫；\n只有在不断的革命理论的发展与革命实践中，工人阶级的斗争才能完成从**自发**到**自觉**的转变，\n而反过来，承认朴素的**自发**的“仇富”感情的合理性，也是推动无产阶级转向**自觉**的阶级斗争的重要条件之一。", "timestamp": 1611936742, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 3, "pid": 202276, "reply": 16, "tag": null, "text": "不是 为啥仇富啊，有钱好香呀", "timestamp": 1611925219, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1611936743, "url": "", "vote": {}}}